在'''愛爾蘭'''，相較於非同志公民，'''女同性戀者、男同性戀者、雙性戀者與跨性別者（LGBT）'''面臨更多法律層面的挑戰和質疑。同性戀自1993年始為合法化，愛爾蘭也立法規範各種基於性傾向的歧視，並禁止煽動性傾向相關仇恨；近20年來，愛爾蘭政府更致力於大幅擴展同志權益。

根據2008年民調，超過84%的愛爾蘭人支持同性伴侶的世俗婚姻或公民結合，其中58%的人同意同性伴侶得在戶籍登記處合法登記，擁有完整的婚姻權利。擁護同性伴侶應僅限公民結合的人數則從33%掉到26%<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.breakingnews.ie/ireland/mhojojeyauid/ |publisher=BreakingNews.ie |title=Increased support for gay marriage – Survey |date=2008-03-31 |language=en |accessdate=2011-06-18 |archive-date=2014-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018211155/http://www.breakingnews.ie/ireland/mhojojeyauid/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在隨後由《[[愛爾蘭時報|愛爾蘭時報]]》主辦的民調中，支持同性婚姻者達63%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://scripts.ireland.com/polls/breaking/index.cfm?fuseaction=yesnopoll&pollid=8376&subsiteid=356 |title=Do you think that same-sex marriage should be allowed in Ireland? – News poll |publisher=''[[愛爾蘭時報|The Irish Times]]'' |date= |accessdate=2009-07-09 |language=en |archive-date=2009-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090111183325/http://scripts.ireland.com/polls/breaking/index.cfm?fuseaction=yesnopoll&pollid=8376&subsiteid=356 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2011年3月的《[[星期日泰晤士報|星期日泰晤士報]]》民調顯示，73%的愛爾蘭人支持同性伴侶應有完整的世俗婚姻權利<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gcn.ie/feature.aspx?sectionid=14&articleid=3182 |title=Poll: Three-Quarters In Favour Of Gay Marriage |work=Gay Community News |accessdate=2011-06-18 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329075724/http://www.gcn.ie/feature.aspx?sectionid=14&articleid=3182 |archivedate=2012-03-29 }}</ref>。

2010年7月，[[愛爾蘭眾議院|愛爾蘭眾議院]]（{{lang-ga|Dáil}}）和[[愛爾蘭參議院|參議院]]（{{lang|ga|Seanad}}）通過《2010年公民結合暨同居者之特定權利與義務法案》，承認同性伴侶的公民結合。法案在眾議院時不須投票、直接通過所有階段，參議院則以48票對4票通過法案。法案獲得所有政黨的支持，僅少數個別政客對此立法表示責難<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/10484404.stm |title=Civil partnership bill backed by Irish politicians |publisher=BBC News |date=2010-07-01 |accessdate=2010-07-11 |language=en |archive-date=2010-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100704080439/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/10484404.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年7月19日，總統[[瑪麗·麥亞烈斯|瑪麗·麥亞烈斯]]簽署法案<ref name="irishtimes1">{{cite web |url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2010/0719/breaking29.html |title=Civil Partnership Bill signed into law |publisher=The Irish Times |date=2010-07-19 |accessdate=2011-01-09 |language=en |archive-date=2012-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021134438/http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2010/0719/breaking29.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年12月23日，司法部長為法案簽署生效命令。法案自2011年1月1日始生效，之後男女同性戀伴侶便可至戶籍登記處註冊為伴侶關係<ref>{{cite web|last=Connolly |first=Niamh |url=http://www.thepost.ie/news/ireland/civil-unions-will-have-to-wait-until-2011-50437.html |title=Civil unions will have to wait until 2011 |publisher=Thepost.ie |date=2010-07-11 |accessdate=2011-01-09 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111001050017/http://www.thepost.ie/news/ireland/civil-unions-will-have-to-wait-until-2011-50437.html |archivedate=2011-10-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2010/0702/breaking4.html?via=mr |title=Civil Partnership Bill |publisher=Irish Times |date=2010-07-02 |accessdate=2011-06-19 |language=en |archive-date=2012-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021093432/http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/breaking/2010/0702/breaking4.html?via=mr |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於愛爾蘭對所有公民婚典儀式訂有三個月的等待期，預估首場公民結合婚禮將於4月舉行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.justice.ie/en/JELR/Pages/Ahern%20announces%20commencement%20of%20Civil%20Partnership%20and%20Cohabitants%20Act |title=Ahern announces commencement of Civil Partnership and Cohabitants Act |publisher=Justice.ie |date= |accessdate=2011-01-09 |language=en |archive-date=2019-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191018232519/http://www.justice.ie/en/JELR/Pages/Ahern%20announces%20commencement%20of%20Civil%20Partnership%20and%20Cohabitants%20Act |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年2月7日，第一個公民伴侶關係誕生，由一對男同志伴侶註冊<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.irishexaminer.com/ireland/kfeyojsncwey/rss2/ |author=Scott Millar |title=First civil partnership ceremony for same-sex couple |publisher=irishexaminer.com |date=2011-02-21 |accessdate=2011-06-19 |language=en |archive-date=2019-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201155356/https://www.irishexaminer.com/ireland/kfeyojsncwey/rss2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第一場根據法案結合、公開慶祝的愛爾蘭公民伴侶的活動儀式則於2011年4月5日在都柏林舉行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rte.ie/news/2011/0405/civilpartnership.html |title=First Irish public civil partnership services |publisher=RTÉ News |date=2011-04-05 |accessdate=2011-06-19 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830091056/http://www.rte.ie/news/2011/0405/civilpartnership.html |archivedate=2011-08-30 }}</ref>。

2015年5月22日愛爾蘭舉行同性婚姻入憲公投，在43個選區當中，42個都支持修改憲法。62%的贊成票使同性婚姻通過，並讓愛爾蘭成為第一個以修憲公投通過同性婚姻的國家。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thenewslens.com/post/167396/ |title=小島的驕傲：愛爾蘭大比數通過同性婚姻合法化 |publisher=The News Lens |date=2015-05-24 |accessdate=2015-05-25 |language=ch |archive-date=2015-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150524233551/http://www.thenewslens.com/post/167396/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

